@startuml odh-labs_predictive-maint
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "User" as user
rectangle "Web Interface" as web
rectangle "Event Producer (Node.js)" as producer
rectangle "Kafka Cluster" as kafka
rectangle "Consumer App" as consumer
rectangle "Seldon Core" as seldon
rectangle "MinIO Storage" as minio
rectangle "OpenShift Cluster" as openshift

user --> web : Views predictions
web --> minio : Fetches results
producer --> kafka : Streams images
kafka --> consumer : Subscribes to topic
consumer --> seldon : Calls model API
seldon --> openshift : Deployed on
consumer --> minio : Stores results
openshift --> kafka : Hosts
openshift --> minio : Hosts
openshift --> seldon : Manages

note right of kafka
  Strimzi Operator manages
  Kafka deployment
end note

note right of seldon
  Exposes model as REST API
  with autoscaling
end note

note left of minio
  Stores:
  - Model artifacts
  - Inference results
  - Dashboard data
end note
@enduml